data.description: This first level condo in beautiful Admirals Point Gated Community is a charming and comfortable abode, featuring three bedrooms and two baths. The unit comes with a convenient two-car garage, offering ample parking space and added security for your vehicles. Step inside this cozy condo and you'll immediately appreciate the tasteful decor and thoughtful layout. The living area is spacious and inviting, with a cozy ambiance perfect for relaxing. The kitchen is well-appointed, with sleek appliances and ample storage space for all your culinary needs. The bedrooms are well-sized and comfortable, offering plenty of privacy and tranquility. One of the best features of this condo is the community amenities. You'll have access to a sparkling pool and relaxing spa, perfect for cooling off on hot summer days or unwinding after a long day at work.
